APK Signer is a ROM Zip Tool which will sign your Rom zip files with a keystore basically the same as signing a APK File

Instructions:

1. Simply place the desired ROM.zip file into the root of the dir IE the same folder as the bat files

2. RENAME the ROM.zip to update.zip

3. Run the disired signing script depending on which java JDK you have installed on your pc

MAke sure you have your enviroment varable Java_Home set to your Currently installed JDK before running this script or else you will not be able to sign anything with this script.